Nigthlight::

Nightlight looked Rodimus went "Come back soon, my love" shet 
thought. 

When she liked to speak with new comer, she noticed that he had 
gone "Wait!!, wait!" she said "Where're you???, where... ?"

She looked around, unsure what to do.
